  schema:name "Dual Power" ;
  schema:description "The strategy of building alternative institutions — food systems, mutual aid networks, conflict resolution, cooperative economies — that meet real needs outside the state and capitalism, making existing power arrangements unnecessary rather than seizing them." ;
